edu.mit.csail.sdg.alloy4

Class Pos

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mit.csail.sdg.alloy4.Pos
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class Pos
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Immutable; stores the filename and line/column position.

    Invariant: filename!=null && x>0 && y>0 && ((y2>y && x2>0) || (y2==y && x2>=x))

    Thread Safety: Safe (since objects of this class are immutable).

    The secondary position is part of the span. I.e. it points to the last position in the stream that is spanned by this position. I.e. it the x2/y2 pair is inclusive

    See Also:
